item.description:
        
          
            Requirement I want to have a daily mail including currency exchange rate information.
Mail subject: include the exchange rate in the mail subject. Mail content: Has some links to banks' exchange rate page. Include some exchange rate history chart. Solution Use ifttt.com
Create a new Applet on IFTTT
Add a new &quot;If This&quot;
Choose &quot;finance&quot; service
Choose &quot;Today's exchange rate report&quot;
Choose the input/output currency and trigger time.
Add a new &quot;Then That&quot;
